import React from 'react';

const SoccerBall = ({ size = 60 }) => {
  return (
    <svg width={size} height={size} viewBox="0 0 100 100" style={{ display: 'inline-block' }}>
      {/* Main ball circle */}
      <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="48" fill="white" stroke="black" strokeWidth="2"/>
      
      {/* Pentagon in center */}
      <polygon 
        points="50,20 65,35 58,55 42,55 35,35" 
        fill="black" 
        stroke="black" 
        strokeWidth="1"
      />
      
      {/* Hexagons around pentagon */}
      <polygon 
        points="50,20 35,35 25,25 35,15 50,20" 
        fill="white" 
        stroke="black" 
        strokeWidth="1"
      />
      <polygon 
        points="50,20 65,35 75,25 65,15 50,20" 
        fill="white" 
        stroke="black" 
        strokeWidth="1"
      />
      <polygon 
        points="35,35 42,55 25,65 15,50 25,35 35,35" 
        fill="white" 
        stroke="black" 
        strokeWidth="1"
      />
      <polygon 
        points="65,35 75,50 85,65 58,55 65,35" 
        fill="white" 
        stroke="black" 
        strokeWidth="1"
      />
      <polygon 
        points="42,55 58,55 65,75 50,85 35,75 42,55" 
        fill="white" 
        stroke="black" 
        strokeWidth="1"
      />
    </svg>
  );
};

export default SoccerBall;
